Create a new Circles Org account for the receiving account. Orgs are best suited for accepting payments from Circles Users. Learn more about Circles Orgs
here
arrow-up-right
Amount (CRC) → how much
Description → your payment reference (example: membership-payment)
Then:
Click Open in Gnosis app (or Show QR)
In the app, click Start monitoring
Complete payment in Gnosis App
Wait for transaction to be confirmed
Tip: always use a unique description(data) each time (like an order ID or member ID). This is what will be used to identify the payment.
